Harman International Industries, Inc. (USA)



Published: April 1, 2015
Content info: 131 Pages














Description

This report presents quick facts about Harman International Industries, Inc., which is principally involved in Audio Products, Lighting Solutions and Electronic Systems Businesses. Illustrated with 110 tables, the report showcases the company's recent news stories and events, sales performance, key markets and market position as against its competitors operating in the industry.



