            Product description        




                    Harman's legendary brands have been introducing important innovations in home entertainment for more than 50 years, and we continue to develop new ways of further enriching the audio/visual experience. From state-of-the-art surround sound systems to Blu-ray Disc and DVD players to whole-house audio systems, Harman is dedicated to raising home entertainment to ever-higher levels of technical sophistication and ease of use.

We'll also keep you entertained on the go with a wide variety of accessories to enrich the sound of your iPod®, mobile phone or other portable music system. Our dynamic multimedia speaker systems turn any computer into a high-fidelity experience for music and gaming enthusiasts, and our premium home theater systems turn any evening with the family into an exciting night at the cinema. Kick back, relax, and enjoy the show with the legendary sounds of Harman.                







